    tldr: "Model financial impact of technical delays, product failures, and engineering challenges on your runway and fundraising timeline.",
    metaDescription: "Technical risk scenarios for startups: model product launch delays. Plan for engineering risks and timeline slippage.",
    keywords: ["product development", "technical risk", "launch delay", "engineering risk", "product roadmap"],
