    readTime: "8 min read",
    tldr: "Discover systematic approaches to improve gross margin through pricing optimization, cost of goods sold reduction, and operational efficiency, critical for startup unit economics.",
    metaDescription: "Improve startup gross margin with pricing strategy, COGS optimization, and operational efficiency tactics that drive profitability.",
